<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<span id="docs-internal-guid-6f78d4e8-b6a9-3fff-0ef7-d27384e3877a"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="1"><br></font></span></p><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><tbody><tr><td width="600" height="170" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff_footer1_151014.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff_footer1_151014.jpg" width="600" height="170" alt="" border="0" style="display: block;"></a></td></tr></tbody></table><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="1">Please do not respond to this email. The email was sent from an unattended mailbox and responses are not reviewed. Please instead contact us on seasonalroles@the-challenge.org.</font></span></p></span>]]></td>
</tr>
<tr valign="top" height="300" >
<td tEditID="c1r2" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r2" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<span id="docs-internal-guid-678969b4-a189-a0b9-0355-a0ba66473fe3" style="line-height: 17.94px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">The first wave of this summer's NCS programme kicks off in less than two months - before you can start your role, we just need a few more pieces of information from you.</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Bank and tax information</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">The 'Bank details' and 'Tax information' sections of the <u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/EssentialInformation.aspx">Essential Information</a></u> page are now open for you to complete with your current and up-to-date tax and payment information.</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">Please <u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/Login.aspx">log into the staffing website</a></u> and enter your bank details and make a tax declaration <b>by 20th May 2016</b>. Failure to do so could result in your wage being paid late or incorrectly.</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Making a tax declaration</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">In order to generate a tax code for you, you need to either send us your P45 (please read on) or make a tax declaration. To make a tax declaration, you'll need to read through three statements, and indicate which statement will be most applicable to your circumstances<b> when your employment with The Challenge commences</b>. </font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">If you are unsure which statement you should choose, select the statement which is most applicable to your current circumstances - it's better to have submitted something than nothing at all!</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Sending in your P45 Form</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">Alternatively, if you have a P45 Form dated from <b>6th April 2016</b> (new tax year), you can simply send it to our payroll partners. Further instructions can be found on the <u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/EssentialInformation.aspx">Essential Information page</a></u>. </font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>What else?</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">If you haven't completed your <b><u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/secure/ei/HSI.aspx">Health, Safeguarding and Inclusion form</a></u> </b>on the staffing website yet, please ensure you do so as soon as possible. <b>We must have this information before we can allocate you to any work placements.</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">We'll use this information to ensure that the NCS programme is safe for both you and others while you're working with us - anything you disclose will be treated confidentially. To find out more about how we use this information, please see our <u><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/frequently-asked-questions/">Health, Safeguarding and Inclusion FAQs</a></u>.</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">This information must be filled out on the online form, but if you'd like to discuss any additional needs or safeguarding concerns you might have, you can contact the Inclusion Staffing Team either by email (<u><font color="#3366ff">inclusion.ss@the-challenge.org</font></u>) or by phone (0203 542 2451).</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b>Any questions?</b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><b><br></b></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">If you have any questions about the Health, Safeguarding and Inclusion form, please contact our Inclusion Staffing Team using the information above. </font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">We regret that we cannot help with any tax queries - if you're unsure what tax information you should provide us with, you should contact HMRC directly.</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">As ever, if you have any general questions about your role or the NCS programme, you can contact us on <font color="#3366ff"><u>seasonalroles@the-challenge.org</u></font>.</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">We look forward to seeing you at training!</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2"><br></font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">The Staffing Team</font></p><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font face="Arial" size="2">The Challenge</font></p></span>]]></td>
</tr>
